# Chat App

A full Python chat application with:

- Asyncio TCP server
- MongoDB backend
- Tkinter-based desktop client
- Support for direct messages and group chats
- Friend requests, group invites, presence updates
- One-click run support (via BAT + Docker for MongoDB)

---

## Features

### ðŸ§  Server
- Async Python server using `asyncio`
- MongoDB storage (users, messages, groups, invites)
- Real-time online/offline presence
- Message history caching and undelivered message queue
- Secure authentication with PBKDF2 hashing
- Unique public UIDs (ABCD-1234 style)
- Friend list + group membership sync

### ðŸ’¬ Client
- Tkinter UI (single executable possible using PyInstaller)
- Login + Registration
- DM and Group chat
- Send/receive messages in real time
- Friend requests + group invites popup window
- Online status indicators
- Dropdown UI for friend and group selection
- Right-side rendering for local messages, left-side for incoming messages

---

